title: Analysis of enhanced_people-100.xlsx
content: Analysis of the enhanced_people-100.xlsx file has been performed. The columns have been described and potential insights have been identified. A text file containing the column descriptions and potential insights has been created. Suggested categorizations include demographic, geographic, professional and contact. Suggested visualizations include pie charts for gender distribution, histograms for age distribution, bar charts for job title distribution, and bar charts for common email domains.
